The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | 3 die in accident
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       3 die in accident
          A STAFF REPORTER                              
	Three persons died and as many were injured after their city-bound car collided with a bus at Heria, in East Midnapore, on Monday. The deceased are Anil Saha, 40, Tirumari Verma, 25, (both residents of Phoolbagan) and Santosh Kumar Soni, 40, of Bihar.                                                                                                                                                                          
